An R package implementing methods to construct priors from historical data.

For examples see
https://igrave.github.io/StudyPrior/Binomial_knitr.pdf
https://igrave.github.io/StudyPrior/Workshop/

To install
> devtools::install_github('igrave/StudyPrior/StudyPrior')

See https://arxiv.org/abs/1708.08239 for more details.